Adapted from the 10th episode of the Hanna Barbera cartoon series.

On the run from Injun Joe, Tom, Huck and Becky get lost in the desert, and are met by Thut who seeks his lost Marna. The three are taken to the Typhonian Pharaoh, by Troglodytes, for a deadly trial. They manage to summon Thut who ends his 5,000 year search for Marna and shows the three the way out.
name: The Curse of Thut
